---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About StackSignal" description="We're developers who got tired of biased reviews. Here's who we are and why we started StackSignal.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-[#0F172A] text-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span class="bg-[#3B82F6]/20 text-[#3B82F6] text-sm font-mono px-4 py-1 rounded">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-users mr-2"></i>about
        </span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">About StackSignal</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-400 max-w-2xl">
        We're developers who got tired of biased reviews. Here's our story.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0F172A] mb-4">Signal Over Noise</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Every tech review site seems to love every tool they write about. That's because most are just chasing affiliate commissions, ranking whatever pays the best regardless of quality.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          We built StackSignal because we wanted something different: <strong class="text-[#0F172A]">honest reviews from people who actually use these tools</strong>.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0F172A] mb-4 mt-10">Our Testing Process</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Every tool we review gets real-world testing. Not a quick demo, not a feature checklistâ€”actual use in real projects for at least 2 weeks. We measure performance, document annoyances, and call out when the marketing doesn't match reality.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-[#F1F5F9] rounded-xl p-6 my-8 border border-slate-200">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#0F172A] mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-handshake text-[#3B82F6]"></i> Our Promise
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-600">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#10B981] mt-1"></i>
              <span>Companies cannot pay for positive reviews</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#10B981] mt-1"></i>
              <span>We disclose affiliate relationships clearly</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#10B981] mt-1"></i>
              <span>If a tool sucks, we'll tell you</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#10B981] mt-1"></i>
              <span>We update reviews when products change</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0F172A] mb-4 mt-10">Get in Touch</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Have feedback? Found an error? Want us to review something specific? Reach out:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-600">
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-envelope text-[#3B82F6] mr-2"></i> hello@stacksignal.io</li>
          <li><i class="fa-brands fa-x-twitter text-[#3B82F6] mr-2"></i> @stacksignal</li>
          <li><i class="fa-brands fa-discord text-[#3B82F6] mr-2"></i> discord.gg/stacksignal</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
